  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced yellow pepper and cook for 3-4 minutes until slightly tender.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook for 4-5 minutes until translucent.",
    "Add the cubed potatoes and cook for 5-7 minutes until they start to brown.",
    "In a small bowl, mix the miso paste with a little water until it forms a smooth paste.",
    "Add the miso paste to the pan and stir well to combine.",
    "Continue cooking for another 5-7 minutes until the potatoes are tender.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley if desired."
